{
  "name": "Eiffel Tower",
  "formatted_address": "Av. Gustave Eiffel, 75007 Paris, France",
  "location": {
    "lat": 48.85837009999999,
    "lng": 2.2944813
  },
  "website": "https://www.toureiffel.paris/fr",
  "rating": 4.7,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "nure SK",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116022119099285322840/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5bdBHj-KQv5jEDuQI5ZOWs9TBm2IVbq6C6b8Z1gCJyXVaX0mc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a week ago",
      "text": "A masterpiece in city of Romance!!! Busy as we went during the summer holidays but nice area to relax with a picnic.\n\nBe careful as there is a lot of folks walking around to pick pocket and also pester tourists.\n\nYou must visit and enter the tower. Lovely views when near by and just impressive to visit.",
      "time": 1756580611,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Nyasha Drinkwater",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115781123117973690735/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDUdlewoo1fI7SD-JGuvYuPXr9C3tLnDKmnhx8G5jXJGLS5yYrKQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "The Eiffel Tower is absolutely magical both during the day and at night. In the daytime, the views from the top are breathtaking.  Paris stretches out in every direction, and it’s worth every step of the climb. My young kids managed it easily, so don’t be put off, it’s very doable for families. The tickets are great value too! only €14.50 for adults and €7 for children. For such an iconic landmark, that’s fantastic!\n\nAt night, the Eiffel Tower transforms into something truly spectacular. Every hour, on the hour, it sparkles for five minutes, and the sight is unforgettable, like something out of a fairytale. Standing beneath it while it twinkles is one of those “wow” moments you’ll never forget.\n\nHighly recommend visiting both by day and night. It’s an absolute must when in Paris!",
      "time": 1755861535,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "betty eshete",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106670826366117679207/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWa2QJ_aqvG6z0epNssM2Yv3iZ0I0FSjjoj4JjpR5PnLwoCNYoC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "a week ago",
      "text": "The Eiffel Tower is truly a must-visit landmark in Paris. I highly recommend going to the top floor in the evening, where the panoramic view of the entire city is simply breathtaking. Exploring this iconic piece of history is an unforgettable experience. During my 15-day stay in Paris, I visited four times — and each visit felt just as remarkable as the first. It’s an attraction that never loses its charm.",
      "time": 1756497663,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Ayat Tadjalli",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109666069180229410875/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwWWSE7CGuKumEsnjjOKduzQCN9s8CIR3Dbpm3cEVowEVtfhBN=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "Visiting the Eiffel Tower was an absolutely unforgettable experience! The sheer beauty and grandeur of this iconic landmark left me amazed from the moment I saw it. Whether you’re standing at the base admiring its incredible structure or taking in the breathtaking panoramic views of Paris from the top, it truly feels magical.\n\nThe atmosphere is vibrant both during the day and at night, especially when the tower sparkles with its famous light show. It’s not just a monument—it’s a symbol of Paris and a must-see for anyone visiting the city.\n\nI highly recommend adding the Eiffel Tower to your itinerary. It’s an experience that will stay with you forever!",
      "time": 1755664988,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Taye O",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109854090653580688174/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIZJ07O5gE2NVKBCJrCUHi1hPI6pUi7b7xlb8_dd0MjqYWBg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 weeks ago",
      "text": "Seeing the Eiffel Tower during the day was cool, but  nothing prepared me for the magic of seeing it at night. It's truly a different experience. The hourly sparkles and glittering lights was breathtaking. One of the most beautiful sights I've ever seen. Absolutely unforgettable!",
      "time": 1755657759,
      "translated": false
    }
  ],
