{
  "name": "Australian Cruise Group",
  "formatted_address": "Wharf 5, King St, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia",
  "location": {
    "lat": -33.8676034,
    "lng": 151.2016384
  },
  "formatted_phone_number": "(02) 8296 7351",
  "website": "https://www.australiancruisegroup.com.au/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=gmb&utm_campaign=website_link",
  "rating": 4.4,
  "reviews": [
    {
      "author_name": "Hans Haupt",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113795814594947370431/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2d58ay8D-JXPFhm9OgsEso3UoaYKrC-il0oovph0cVPd3FhYN=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "2 months ago",
      "text": "The Sydney Showboat Prestige Dinner Cruise was exceptional! I booked for my 40th birthday, and was impressed from start to finish. The booking experience was seamless, the food great (there was so much, guests couldn’t finish all the food from the five courses), the entertainment fantastic, and the views of Sydney were sublime. The cruise superseded expectations and was, in my opinion, great value for money. I would highly recommend it to friends and family in the future or to anyone looking for something fun and different to do. Thank you for making my birthday unforgettable!",
      "time": 1749517434,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Adut Lual",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118438074505780002908/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIYDwMV8PsDmPeNVabBMNe6bsHTSe18aQi1VOBLV9tc9OYSEAg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "5 months ago",
      "text": "I booked for 9 people to celebrate my birthday, opting for the unlimited drinks package and VIP seating. The food was amazing. Personally, I don’t eat seafood, so I skipped the entrée, but my guests who did loved it. For the main course, I had the chicken breast, and the presentation along with the mushroom sauce was delicious. The portion size of the main was generous and very filling. Desert was 10/10.\n\nThe entertainment was fantastic, with high-energy dancers who really knew how to put on a show. I also appreciated how organised everything was. We even got to step outside and take pictures, which was a nice touch. I loved how they gave everyone celebrating a chance to come on stage, and the whole crowd celebrated them.\n\nOverall, I had an amazing time, and so did all my guests. I would definitely recommend it – 10/10!",
      "time": 1743995614,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Nikolaus Beattie",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111068364918053006343/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBGLSxm0sTERKG90c55pUTO8YqURk9X6zVCKDH5okfEOY71VRS=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "3 months ago",
      "text": "Took the 2 hour late sailing vivid cruise on the magistic 2 and had a lovely time. They had a sale on and the price at around 45 bucks with a glass of house bubbles on arrival was very reasonable. Ship was good, clean, and plenty of space.\n\nI’ve been on them before and will keep sailing on them.",
      "time": 1748610565,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Reece Sophocleous",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100088692263183194490/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeUKN00ngQwdwWfU1qtXvmUCDBHngk5dX9O-xuQmMYX3s-v_du=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 4,
      "relative_time_description": "2 months ago",
      "text": "Great cruise and dining experience for Valentines’s day. Amazing views of the harbour. We paid for a window upgrade when we booked but obviously so did everyone else because we didn’t get seated at a window seat when we boarded. It wasn’t really a big deal, but we didn’t get refunded for it. Would have been nice if they at least locked out the upgrade once it had been filled. Wouldn’t recommend paying for the window seat upgrade anyway, you can see everything from the middle or if you just go for a walk up on the deck. Other than that it was a great night. Amazing food, staff and entertainment.",
      "time": 1749900206,
      "translated": false
    },
    {
      "author_name": "Emily Evans",
      "author_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104422763078892741526/reviews",
      "language": "en",
      "original_language": "en",
      "profile_photo_url": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDS7qTd4Lrkwj-a7uLn_slKtFu0A-7gAfby9dfERs2C_Nx1g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo",
      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "5 months ago",
      "text": "A fantastic night to celebrate a birthday. The crew made great efforts to make the birthday girl feel special which was a nice touch.\nThe show itself was such fun and the route the boat took was great for seeing the sights and great pictures.\nEverything was really good and I would recommend.",
      "time": 1742941190,
      "translated": false
    }
  ],
